                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method of lithium ion battery electrolyte",
                    "一种锂离子电池电解液的制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a preparation method of a lithium ion battery electrolyte, and belongs to the technical field of batteries. Reacting polyphosphoric acid with anhydrous hydrogen fluoride to obtain a hexafluorophosphoric acid aqueous solution; dehydrating the hexafluorophosphoric acid aqueous solution by using a mixed solution of polyphosphoric acid and pyrophosphoric acid to obtain a mixed acid solution; carrying out gas-liquid separation to obtain a crude product phosphorus pentafluoride gas and orthophosphoric acid mixed solution; heating and dehydrating the orthophosphoric acid mixed solution; introducing the crude phosphorus pentafluoride gas into fuming sulfuric acid to obtain high-purity phosphorus pentafluoride gas; the method comprises the following steps: mixing a lithium salt, an organic solvent and high-purity phosphorus pentafluoride gas, and deacidifying and dehydrating after reaction to obtain the lithium ion battery electrolyte. According to the method disclosed by the invention, less polluting gas is discharged in the production process, the chromaticity of the electrolyte is high, the content of lithium hexafluorophosphate is high, the moisture content is low, and the production cost is low."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开一种锂离子电池电解液的制备方法，属于电池技术领域，包括以下步骤；将多聚磷酸和无水氟化氢反应后得到六氟磷酸水溶液；将所述六氟磷酸水溶液用多聚磷酸和焦磷酸的混合液脱水，得到混酸溶液；进行气液分离，得到粗品五氟化磷气体与正磷酸混合液；将正磷酸混合液加热脱水；将粗品五氟化磷气体充入发烟硫酸，得到高纯度五氟化磷气体；将锂盐、有机溶剂、高纯度五氟化磷气体混合，反应结束后经脱酸脱水后得到锂离子电池电解液。本发明的方法生产过程中排放的污染性气体少，电解液色度高，六氟磷酸锂含量高，水分含量低，生产成本低。"
                }
            ]
